  <title>Add Stock Symbos</title>
  
  <p>
    You can add stock symbols by editing the <file>~/.config/indicator-stocks/symbols.conf</file> file.
    Please note that you need to restart <app>indicator-stocks</app> after editing this file
	for the changes to take effect.
  </p>

  <note style="tip">
    <p>
      You can find the stock symbol for a company 
      at <link href="http://finance.yahoo.com/">Yahoo Finance</link>.
    </p>
  </note>

  <note style="important">
    <p>Add <em>one</em> symbol per line.</p>
  </note>
  
  <listing>
    <title>Example: <file>~/.config/indicator-stocks/symbols.conf</file></title>
<code>
AMD.DE
INTC
</code>
  </listing>

  <p>
    In the above example <code>AMD.DE</code> is the symbol for
    <em>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. (Equity-XETRA)</em>.
    <code>INTC</code> is the symbol for <em>Intel Corporation (Equity-NASDAQ)</em>.
  </p>

